      "noteId": "68f5a72b000000000302dbd5",
      "title": "Yosemite Valley 风景点 停车位置",
      "desc": "Valley里是单行线，并且不好停车，错过景点就要绕一大圈回来，堵车时太坑。所以我汇总了各风景点的比较好的停车位置（图1）：\n\t\n[一R]37°42'58.5\"N 119°39'58.1\"W\n景点：Pohono Bridge\n\t\n[二R] Bridalveil Falls Trailhead\n景点：Bridalveil Fall 图2\n\t\n[三R] Cathedral Beach Picnic Area, TUOLUMNE MEADOWS, CA 95389\n景点：Cathedral Beach 图3\n\t\n[四R]Sentinel Beach Picnic Area, Yosemite National Park, Wawona, CA 95389\n景点：Sentinel Beach\n\t\n[五R] 37°44'10.4\"N 119°35'58.0\"W (路左侧趴车位)\n景点：Swinging Bridge 图4-6\n\t\n[六R] Yosemite Valley Chapel, 9000 Southside Dr, Yosemite Valley, CA 95389\n景点：Yosemite Valley Chapel 图7\n\t\n[七R] 37°44'38.6\"N 119°35'23.8\"W （小停车场，只能从Southside Dr进，开出只能去Northside Dr方向）；或者开到 Yosemite Village Parking, Yosemite Valley, CA 95389（大停车场，之后开去northside或者southside都可）\n可以看两个景点：\nCook’s Meadow trail 图8-9\nSentinel Bridge 图10-11\n\t\n[八R]37°44'44.5\"N 119°35'49.3”W：左手边有parking的入口。\n景点：Lower Yosemite Fall 图12\n\t\n[九R] El Capitan Meadow, California 95389 (路左平趴趴车位)\n景点：El Cap Meadow 图13-14\n\t\n[一R][零R] 37°43'02.4\"N 119°39'42.9\"W (路左侧小停车场)\n景点：Valley View 图15\n\t\n#Yosemite[话题]# #Yosemite攻略[话题]# #优胜美地[话题]# #优胜美地攻略[话题]#  #YosemiteValley[话题]#",
